org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.graph
Class AeGraphProperties

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Dictionary
      java.util.Hashtable
          java.util.Properties
              org.activebpel.rt.bpeladmin.war.graph.AeGraphProperties
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.util.Map, java.io.Serializable
public class AeGraphProperties
extends java.util.Properties

Reads the graph color and layout properties from graph.properties resource. The properties may be overrride via the graph image servlet init properties. Note: If a new property is add, then new property with the default value must be entered in the graph.properties resource resource file.
